snippet.title: VGA 2011: Amazing Spider-Man Exclusive Debut Trailer
snippet.description:
Spidey slings his way back through the streets of New York in The Amazing Spider-Man!  Check out the announcement trailer from the Spike Video Game Awards 2011!

Get more VGA action at http://vga.spike.com
